node.text:
The @contitourgold is BACK💫

Following the World Relays earlier this year, we’re returning to Silesia for the @memorial_kamili_skolimowskiej 🌪

Watch LIVE at 16:50 CEST Sunday Sep 5th on the World Athletics YouTube channel 🎥

#ContinentalTourGold #Athletics #TrackAndField #Track

node.text:
It's Mondo's 𝘮𝘶𝘯𝘥𝘰, we're just living in it! 👀

@mondo_duplantis 🇸🇪 clears 6.05m to break the meeting record and to take the win at #BrusselsDL!

#Athletics #TrackAndField 

📷 @matthewquine / @diamondleagueathletics (second and third photo)

node.text:
"I was really excited to run here," said 18-year-old @christine_mboma 🇳🇦 after her 200m victory at #BrusselsDL.

"It was my first #DiamondLeague experience and to be able to win against such a strong field is great!"

📷 @matthewquine / @diamondleagueathletics

node.text:
History: ✅

@fkerley99 🇺🇸 wins the men's 100m and becomes 𝘁𝗵𝗲 𝗳𝗶𝗿𝘀𝘁 𝗺𝗮𝗻 𝘁𝗼 𝘄𝗶𝗻 𝗼𝘃𝗲𝗿 𝟭𝟬𝟬𝗺, 𝟮𝟬𝟬𝗺 𝗮𝗻𝗱 𝟰𝟬𝟬𝗺 in the #DiamondLeague! 

#BrusselsDL 

📷 @matthewquine / @diamondleagueathletics

node.text:

node.text:
Still in awe 30 years later! 

Tomorrow, Mike Powell 🇺🇸 will enter the @allianzmemorialvandamme’s Hall Of Fame and get a statue in his name. 

He’s won six times here and his world record from the 1991 #WorldAthleticsChamps in Tokyo is still standing! 

Legend. 💫 

#DiamondLeague #Athletics #WorldAthletics #TrackAndField #LongJump
